  "title": "Accounts Assistant (Woodland/Food MFG Co./Microsoft Dynamics 365 )",
  "description": "<ul><li>Prepare Audit schedule</li><li>Processing all invoices</li><li>checking on daily salesman report of sales</li><li>Perform data entry and other adhoc duties</li><li>Record payments, invoices, and journal entries into the accounting system</li><li>Review and verify monthly petty cash statements and claims</li><li>Maintain daily cash book schedules, monitor cash flow and balances, and perform bank reconciliations</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Accounting</li><li>1-2 years of Accounting experience</li><li>Familiar with MS Dynamic 365</li><li>Proficient in MS Excel</li></ul><p><br /><strong>5 days work week</strong><br /><strong>Woodland Area</strong><br /><strong>Food Manufacturing Co.</strong><br /><strong></strong><br />Interested candidates, please send a detailed resume via email to <a href=\"mailto:hr@tempserv.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>hr@tempserv.com.sg</strong></a></p><p><strong>Tempserv Pte Ltd</strong><br />License No: 06C3745<br /><strong>Attention: Audris Teo / EA Personnel No: R1102063</strong></p>",
